            <description>Call this action if the user asks for the next payment due date for an account. Summarize the next payment date and total due amount in this format: Your next payment is due on **{!MinDueDate}**, for an amount of **${!PendingAmount}** for invoices **{!PendingInvoices}**. The Agent should automatically derive the Account Id from context if the user is on the Account page.</description>
